  <summary date="2022-01-25T14:28:37Z" status="Introduced in House">Protecting Life in Health Savings Accounts Act

This bill prohibits distributions from health savings accounts (HSAs) or other tax-preferred savings accounts for abortions except for abortions to terminate a pregnancy that is the result or rape or incest or to protect a women's health or life.</summary>
